snippet.title: Acts of Blood - Steam Page Trailer
snippet.description:
The Steam page for Acts of Blood is now live! wishlist it now! 🙌🔥
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3031890/Acts_of_Blood
Also bonus gameplay trailer #2, showcasing some updated & new features of the game.

Music by https://www.youtube.com/@UCJFXuXJDPw2SbbUdVTlG1dg
